10:43.250 --> 10:45.667
Sophia, so maybe take comfort in that.

10:45.750 --> 10:46.709
Matt, hey, listen.

10:46.792 --> 10:49.417
Dad is at St. Fran's.

10:46.792 --> 10:49.417
