11:23.417 --> 11:24.542
I'm so sorry.

11:24.625 --> 11:25.834
-Dad?

11:24.625 --> 11:25.834
-Oh, no! No.

11:25.917 --> 11:27.250
-How you do...

11:25.917 --> 11:27.250
-(John groaning)

