11:37.208 --> 11:38.417
Are you okay, Pop-Pop?

11:38.917 --> 11:40.125
(groaning)

11:40.208 --> 11:41.291
-You should go.

11:40.208 --> 11:41.291
-You're not helping.

11:42.709 --> 11:45.333
Just pull the plug.

11:42.709 --> 11:45.333
I don't want to live anymore.

11:48.291 --> 11:49.542
