13:05.750 --> 13:07.208
My life is a lie.

13:07.917 --> 13:09.166
Just end it.

13:09.542 --> 13:10.750
Just end it!

13:12.959 --> 13:14.959
Hm. Now I'm hot.

13:15.250 --> 13:17.083
I'm so sorry I didn't tell you.

13:17.166 --> 13:19.542
I-I-I'm supposed to be

13:17.166 --> 13:19.542
