13:25.041 --> 13:27.083
Have nothing but a soggy breadstick?

13:27.166 --> 13:30.000
But honey, they love you.

13:27.166 --> 13:30.000
That's why they're all here.

13:30.083 --> 13:31.917
And they'll look up to you no matter what.

13:33.917 --> 13:34.959
What about you?

13:35.041 --> 13:36.709
Well, I don't care

13:35.041 --> 13:36.709
