14:24.041 --> 14:25.542
I took the easier way out, so...

14:28.709 --> 14:29.542
It's good coffee.

14:29.625 --> 14:30.583
Yeah.

14:30.667 --> 14:32.625
As helpful as you've been this morning,

14:32.709 --> 14:34.583
I feel like maybe I'll change her

14:34.667 --> 14:36.417
