14:36.500 --> 14:38.542
-You're gonna drive away, aren't you?

14:36.500 --> 14:38.542
-No.

14:39.875 --> 14:41.208
Take my keys just in case.

14:41.542 --> 14:42.458
(car door closes)

14:42.542 --> 14:44.458
(indistinct chattering)

14:44.542 --> 14:46.291
-Hey!

14:44.542 --> 14:46.291
-(door closes)

14:46.375 --> 14:49.000
ALL: Hey!

14:49.083 --> 14:49.917
What's this?

14:50.000 --> 14:53.959
