14:54.041 --> 14:57.917
so we thought it'd be wonderful

14:54.041 --> 14:57.917
to shower you with gifts.

14:58.000 --> 14:58.875
Uh, Mom...

14:58.959 --> 15:01.000
No, no, it's just a few. Just a few.

15:01.083 --> 15:04.583
I know it's a little early,

15:01.083 --> 15:04.583
