Oh, this frosting! Oh, that is so good.

17:10.667 --> 17:11.875
So good! Do you want some?

17:11.959 --> 17:14.500
Uh, no, I generally prefer a-a plate...

17:14.583 --> 17:15.959
-to a human hand.

17:14.583 --> 17:15.959
-HEATHER: Mm.

17:16.041 --> 17:17.000
Oh, huh. Fancy.

17:17.083 --> 17:18.667
-Really?

17:17.083 --> 17:18.667
-Yeah.

17:18.750 --> 17:19.959
Uh, you know what, I'll have some.

17:20.041 --> 17:20.875
-It's so good.

17:20.041 --> 17:20.875
-GREG: Yeah?

17:20.959 --> 17:22.917
-HEATHER: Yeah, get in there.

17:20.959 --> 17:22.917
-Oh, my God, Greg, please.

17:23.583 --> 17:24.583
HEATHER: Just get in there.

17:24.667 --> 17:26.625
Um, honey, I'll just be in the...

17:26.709 --> 17:28.834
-GREG (muffled): Mm-hm, okay. Love you.

17:26.709 --> 17:28.834
-Okay, okay.

17:31.583 --> 17:33.083
What are you doing?

17:33.458 --> 17:34.625
Just act normal!

17:34.709 --> 17:36.709
You know, just people at brunch.

17:36.792 --> 17:38.458
I mean, we do it every weekend.

17:44.917 --> 17:46.834
Oh, a toast to Jen.

17:47.500 --> 17:49.375
-Uh, Dad...

17:47.500 --> 17:49.375
-To me? Me?

17:49.458 --> 17:51.417
Uh, er, um...

17:51.959 --> 17:53.083
What can I say? Uh...

17:53.458 --> 17:55.166
you're a national treasure.

17:55.917 --> 17:57.500
Wow, that's so nice.

17:57.583 --> 18:00.375
So did the hospital say

17:57.583 --> 18:00.375
that you could mix alcohol

18:00.458 --> 18:02.083
