18:02.667 --> 18:04.041
They didn't say I couldn't.

18:04.125 --> 18:07.291
-Right.

18:04.125 --> 18:07.291
-Hey, Jen, where's the diaper bag?

18:07.375 --> 18:09.125
Her tushy got a little mushy.

18:09.208 --> 18:11.291
Oh, listen to me, I'm rhyming again!

18:11.375 --> 18:12.709
(laughs) I'm on a roll.

18:12.792 --> 18:16.166
Clearly. Uh, the only problem

18:12.792 --> 18:16.166
