19:03.750 --> 19:04.834
uh, do this.

19:04.917 --> 19:09.458
You do whatever it is that you need to do,

19:04.917 --> 19:09.458
and to hell with everybody else.

19:10.542 --> 19:13.792
Um, sometimes it-it helps

19:10.542 --> 19:13.792
