19:22.750 --> 19:24.542
I-I didn't know that you had had one.

19:24.625 --> 19:25.875
Yeah, after Matt.

19:25.959 --> 19:26.959
Oh.

19:27.041 --> 19:28.667
Yeah, I still think about it.

