19:32.792 --> 19:36.667
If I hadn't lost that baby,

19:32.792 --> 19:36.667
I wouldn't have had Greg.

19:38.125 --> 19:40.792
And you wouldn't have Lark.

19:42.750 --> 19:44.250
And we wouldn't have you.

19:46.417 --> 19:47.250
Thank you.

